                            convallis. Nunc sed orci a diam ultrices aliquet interdum quis nulla.</p>
                        <ul class="list-inline">
                            <li class="list-inline-item">
                                <h6>Avaliable Color :</h6>
                            </li>
                            <li class="list-inline-item">
                                <p class="text-muted"><strong>White / Black</strong></p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>

                        <h6>Specification:</h6>
